\i Pig:
\i0 \
A player repeatedly throws a die until either a 1 is thrown or the player decides to "hold". If the player throws a 1, they score nothing and it becomes the next player's turn. If the player throws any other number, it is added to their "Pay" total and the player's turn continues. If the player chooses to "hold", their "Pay" total is added to their score, and it becomes the next player's turn. We'll keep track of the Pay for you.\
